<div class="about-bio">
  <p>
    I have a theory: the people most confident they understand the wave are
    usually the ones who didn't see the reef. I write Overfit because precision
    and accuracy aren't the same thing — in machine learning, in architecture,
    or in life.
  </p>
  <p class="about-sep">· · ·</p>
  <p>
    Outside of work I spend my time losing at board games with good friends,
    raising three sons who keep me honest, and married to a woman who has
    watched me be confidently wrong enough times to deserve a medal.
  </p>
